text: El faro (The Lighthouse) is a 1998 Argentine Spanish drama movie directed by Eduardo Mignogna and starring Ingrid Rubio, Norma Aleandro, Jorge Marrale, Ricardo Darín, Norberto Díaz, Mariano Martínez, Paola Krum. ==Other websites== * Category:1998 drama movies Category:Argentine drama movies Category:Spanish drama movies Category:Movies directed by Eduardo Mignogna Category:Movies about sisters Category:Movies set in Uruguay
title: The Lighthouse
